_sText:
This is my version of the famous aim_ak-colt.
It is very simple built.
It is very smooth.
Does not use a lot of performance.
_______________________________________________________________
I made it by my own from scratch which means I did not use Vmex.
You spawn with a rifle above you so you don't have to run back later to pick on up as in the original aim_al-colt.
Worth to play or download to servers.
